Notes: WIAC Championship Semifinal...UWO advances to the tournament final for the
fourth straight year, hosting UW-Whitewater (21-5) in this year's final on
Feb. 26...UWO is the three-time defending WIAC tournament champion...UWO gets
eight points and 12 rebounds from Kokta, UWRF 11 points from Theisen.
